{"segment_id": "shijing__song-minyuxiaozi-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-minyuxiaozi-003", "source_id": "song-minyuxiaozi-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·003.1", "text_original": "敬之敬之，天維顯思。\n命不易哉！無曰高高在上。\n陟降厥士，日監在茲。", "text_normalized": "敬之敬之，天維顯思。\n命不易哉！無曰高高在上。\n陟降厥士，日監在茲。", "notes": "敬之 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-minyuxiaozi-003__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-minyuxiaozi-003", "source_id": "song-minyuxiaozi-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·003.2", "text_original": "維予小子，不聦敬止？\n日就月將，學有緝熙于光明。\n佛時仔肩，示我顯德行。", "text_normalized": "維予小子，不聦敬止？\n日就月將，學有緝熙于光明。\n佛時仔肩，示我顯德行。", "notes": "敬之 Chinese stanza 2."}
